I started adding the iron concentration term in the entity_attribute_location.csv file as stated here #1217. As deleting the line in the csv was deleting the obsoleted term completely, I decided to use the chemical_concentration pattern instead. 
Not sure what the recommendation is when several patterns can be used to add a term.  

@KrishnaTO I believe you can use this PR as an example to add the other terms, for which we have opened tickets. Could you use the pattern (chemical_concentration) to add the terms? Thanks

